sourcesContent:
let searchListContainer = {
  display: "flex",
  margin: "15px 0px 0px 15px",
}

let phoneListContainer = {
  height: "22px",
  display: "flex",
  width: "calc(65vw - 28px)",
  borderRadius: "5px 0px 0px 5px"
}

let phoneListContainerMAC = {
  cursor: "pointer",
  fontSize: "15px",
  textAlign: "center",
  minWidth: "200px",
  maxWidth: "200px",
  color: "white",
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  overflow: "hidden",
  whiteSpace: "nowrap",
  lineHeight: "22px",
  borderRadius: "4px 0px 0px 4px"
}

let phoneListContainerInfo = {
  width: "100%",
  borderStyle: "solid",
  borderLeftStyle: "none",
  borderWidth: "1px",
  borderColor: "#4382BC",
}

let phoneListContainerItems = {
  listStyleType: "none",
  height: "18px",
  display: "flex",
  marginTop: "0px",
  textAlign: "center",
  backgroundColor: "#e8fefd",
  padding: 0,
  zIndex: 2
}

let phoneListContainerItem = {
  fontSize: "15px",
  width: "20%",
  marginLeft: "15px",
  textTransform: "capitalize",
  overflow: "hidden",
  whiteSpace: "nowrap",
  textOverflow: "ellipsis",
  lineHeight: "20px",
}

export {
  phoneListContainer,
  phoneListContainerMAC,
  phoneListContainerInfo,
  phoneListContainerItems,
  phoneListContainerItem,
  searchListContainer
}
